node.text:
If you put on your best behavior...

And you don't drink that much...

And you don't smoke any weed...

And you don't mention how much you play Xbox...

You might end up with a girlfriend... for a minute.

The truth is 9 times out of 10, when we're dating...

We're not dating the individual we met...

We're dating the best version of them.

And those RARELY stick around.

Be YOURSELF and save everyone some time.

Pick your difficult.

node.text:
When you're crashing in an airplane, they’ll tell you to put your own oxygen mask on first.

Why?

Because if you run out of air you can’t help anyone else.

Do that in life.

Do that with business.

Act like you're more relevant.

Act like you're more important than you are currently acting.

Some people can call that selfishness…

I call that intelligence.
